dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Faster, harder, and better than ever. Whether you're describing this Murray Cup's season, or me, your host Trevor Basque, you'd be right. Welcome to the New Horizon Qualifiers.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: We are back and racing in New Horizon. Im Shawn Walker for GSN Murray Cup coverage.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: You can feel the excitment here at New Horizon as we gear up for another Murray Cup race. I'm Shawn Walker, and welcome to the Qualifiers.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Hello ladies and gentlmen, welcome to the New Horizon Speedway in lovely Ellis System for another Murray Cup Qualifier.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Do you feel that? That need to feel g-forces pull blood from your brain? Well, look no further. Racing season is back.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: This is Trevor Basque for Murray Cup racing. Let's go now to today's qualifier.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Hello everyone, this is Trevor Basque, got another surefire heartstopper about to get underway.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to the Murray Cup Qualifier, my name's Trevor Basque.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Hello racers and gearheads, this is Trevor Basque casting live from the New Horizon Raceway.

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: If you've got Murray Cup fever, then you've come to the right place. I'll be your doctor, Trevor Basque, but instead of a cure, I'll be dosing out just more racing fever, or something. I am not a real doctor. On to the race!

dialogue.speaker: c2686a11-67f9-4ca3-aa8f-0524ecd562a1
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome back to Murray Cup racing. Hello, I'm Trevor Basque and let's go straight away to today's qualifier.
